ase continue. Using Tool | Read https://n8n.io/workflows/4762-automate-sleep-meditation-content-creation-with-elevenlabs-v3-and-deepseek-ai/ View Please continue. Using Tool | Search real-time AI meditation script generation API OpenAI GPT personalized relaxation audio View Please continue. Now I'll create a comprehensive system design for your n8n automation that generates on-demand meditation and focus scripts with AI voiceovers and binaural beats. N8n Meditation Audio Generation Automation System Complete Interactive Web App Backend Architecture System Overview Objective: Create on-demand, personalized meditation/focus audio content with spoken work and background binaural beats for different mental states (relaxation, focus, study, stress relief, creativity). Core N8n Workflow Architecture Master Workflow Components Component\tFunction\tAPI Integration\tOutput Trigger Webhook\tReceives user input from web app\tCustom API endpoint\tUser parameters State Analyzer\tDetermines optimal brainwave frequency\tOpenAI GPT-4\tTarget Hz + script type Script Generator\tCreates personalized meditation script\tOpenAI GPT-4\tStructured meditation text Voice Synthesizer\tConverts script to speech\tElevenLabs/OpenAI TTS\tMP3 voice track Binaural Generator\tCreates background frequency audio\tWeb Audio API/Custom\tBackground audio Audio Mixer\tCombines voice + binaural beats\tFFmpeg/Audio API\tFinal mixed audio Storage Manager\tSaves and serves final audio\tAWS S3/Google Drive\tDownload URL Detailed N8n Workflow Design 1. Input Processing Node Copy { \"webhook_trigger\": { \"method\": \"POST\", \"path\": \"/generate-meditation\", \"input_schema\": { \"situation\": \"string\", // e.g., \"need to focus for writing\", \"stressed after meeting\" \"duration\": \"integer\", // minutes (5, 10, 15, 20, 30) \"voice_preference\": \"string\", // \"male\", \"female\", \"calm\", \"energetic\" \"intensity\": \"string\", // \"gentle\", \"medium\", \"deep\" \"background_preference\": \"string\" // \"nature\", \"minimal\", \"binaural_only\" } } } 2. AI State Analysis Node Integration: OpenAI GPT-4 API Copy // N8n Code Node const situation = $json.situation; const intensity = $json.intensity; const prompt = `Analyze this situation and recommend optimal brainwave frequency and meditation approach: Situation: \"${situation}\" Intensity: \"${intensity}\" Return JSON format: { \"target_frequency\": \"Hz value (7-14 alpha, 15-30 beta, 4-7 theta)\", \"meditation_type\": \"relaxation/focus/creativity/stress_relief\", \"script_style\": \"guided_visualization/breathing/progressive_relaxation/mantra\", \"duration_segments\": [\"intro\", \"main\", \"outro\"], \"background_sounds\": \"recommended type\" }`; return { json: { analysis_prompt: prompt, user_input: $json } }; 3. Script Generation Node Integration: OpenAI GPT-4 API Copy // Dynamic Script Generator const analysisResult = $json.ai_analysis; const userDuration = $json.duration; const scriptPrompt = `Create a ${userDuration}-minute ${analysisResult.meditation_type} meditation script for ${analysisResult.script_style}. Requirements: - Include timing cues: [PAUSE 3s], [BREATHE], [SOFT TONE] - Natural pacing for ${analysisResult.target_frequency}Hz brainwave entrainment - Personalized for situation: \"${$json.situation}\" - Professional, calming language - Clear beginning, middle, end structure Format as JSON: { \"intro_script\": \"0-2 minutes introduction text\", \"main_script\": \"Main meditation content with timing cues\", \"outro_script\": \"Gentle return to awareness\", \"total_words\": \"word count\", \"estimated_duration\": \"actual minutes\" }`; 4. Voice Synthesis Node Integration: ElevenLabs API or OpenAI TTS Copy // Voice Generation Configuration const voiceSettings = { \"elevenlabs\": { \"voice_id\": $json.voice_preference === \"male\" ? \"pNInz6obpgDQGcFmaJgB\" : \"EXAVITQu4vr4xnSDxMaL\", \"model_id\": \"eleven_multilingual_v2\", \"voice_settings\": { \"stability\": 0.75, \"similarity_boost\": 0.85, \"style\": 0.2, \"use_speaker_boost\": true } }, \"openai_tts\": { \"model\": \"tts-1-hd\", \"voice\": $json.voice_preference === \"male\" ? \"onyx\" : \"nova\", \"speed\": 0.8  // Slower for meditation } }; 5. Binaural Beat Generator Node Integration: Web Audio API via N8n Code Node Copy // Binaural Beat Generation Function function generateBinauralBeats(targetFreq, duration) { const baseFreq = 200; // Base carrier frequency const beatFreq = targetFreq; // Target brainwave frequency return { left_channel: baseFreq, right_channel: baseFreq + beatFreq, duration: duration * 60, // Convert to seconds amplitude: 0.3, // Background level fade_in: 10, // Seconds fade_out: 10 }; } // Background Sound Selection const backgroundConfig = { \"nature\": { \"sounds\": [\"rain\", \"ocean\", \"forest\"], \"volume\": 0.2 }, \"minimal\": { \"sounds\": [\"white_noise\", \"brown_noise\"], \"volume\": 0.15 }, \"binaural_only\": { \"sounds\": [], \"volume\": 0 } }; Copy 6. Audio Processing & Mixing Node Integration: FFmpeg API or Audio Processing Service Copy // Audio Mixing Configuration const mixingInstructions = { \"voice_track\": { \"volume\": 1.0, \"eq\": { \"low_cut\": \"80Hz\", \"high_boost\": \"slight +2dB at 5kHz\" } }, \"binaural_track\": { \"volume\": 0.3, \"fade_envelope\": \"gradual_increase_first_2min\" }, \"background_track\": { \"volume\": 0.2, \"loop\": true, \"crossfade\": true }, \"master_output\": { \"format\": \"mp3\", \"bitrate\": \"192kbps\", \"normalize\": true } }; Brainwave Frequency Mapping Mental State\tTarget Hz\tBinaural Beat\tScript Focus\tDuration Rec Deep Relaxation\t4-7 Hz (Theta)\t6 Hz\tBody scan, breath awareness\t15-20 min Calm Focus\t8-12 Hz (Alpha)\t10 Hz\tAttention training, visualization\t10-15 min Study Mode\t15-20 Hz (Beta)\t18 Hz\tMemory enhancement, clarity\t8-12 min Creative Flow\t8-10 Hz (Alpha)\t9 Hz\tOpen awareness, imagination\t12-18 min Stress Relief\t6-8 Hz (Theta)\t7 Hz\tProgressive relaxation, release\t15-25 min Peak Performance\t30-40 Hz (Gamma)\t35 Hz\tConcentration, cognitive boost\t5-10 min API Integration Stack Required Services & Costs Service\tPurpose\tMonthly Cost\tUsage Limits OpenAI GPT-4\tScript generation\t$20-100\t500-2500 requests ElevenLabs\tVoice synthesis\t$22-99\t30K-500K characters AWS S3\tAudio storage\t$1-10\t5GB-100GB storage FFmpeg Cloud\tAudio processing\t$15-50\t100-500 processing hours N8n Cloud\tWorkflow hosting\t$20-50\tUnlimited workflows Web Audio API\tBinaural generation\tFree\tUnlimited Total Monthly: $78-309 (scales with usage) Complete N8n Workflow Structure Node Sequence Webhook Trigger → User input reception Code Node → Input validation & parsing OpenAI Node → Situation analysis & recommendations Code Node → Script prompt generation OpenAI Node → Meditation script creation HTTP Node → ElevenLabs voice synthesis Code Node → Binaural beat parameters calculation HTTP Node → Audio generation service call Code Node → Audio mixing instructions HTTP Node → FFmpeg processing API AWS S3 Node → Final audio storage Webhook Response → Return download URL to web app Error Handling Nodes Retry Logic: For API failures Fallback Voices: Alternative TTS services Quality Checks: Audio validation User Notifications: Status updates Web App Integration Points Frontend Interface Elements Copy <!-- Situation Input Interface --> <div class=\"situation-selector\"> <h3>What do you need right now?</h3> <button data-situation=\"focus-writing\">Focus for Writing</button> <button data-situation=\"stress-relief\">Stress Relief</button> <button data-situation=\"study-session\">Study Session</button> <button data-situation=\"creative-block\">Creative Block</button> <button data-situation=\"anxiety-calm\">Anxiety Relief</button> <button data-situation=\"sleep-prep\">Sleep Preparation</button> </div> <!-- Customization Options --> <div class=\"audio-preferences\"> <select name=\"voice\"> <option value=\"calm-female\">Calm Female Voice</option> <option value=\"warm-male\">Warm Male Voice</option> <option value=\"neutral\">Gender Neutral</option> </select> <select name=\"background\"> <option value=\"binaural-only\">Binaural Beats Only</option> <option value=\"nature-sounds\">Nature Sounds</option> <option value=\"ambient-minimal\">Minimal Ambient</option> </select> <input type=\"range\" name=\"intensity\" min=\"1\" max=\"5\" value=\"3\"> <label>Intensity: Gentle ← → Deep</label> </div> API Call Implementation Copy // Web App to N8n Integration async function generateMeditationAudio(userPreferences) { const response = await fetch('YOUR_N8N_WEBHOOK_URL/generate-meditation', { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Authorization': 'Bearer YOUR_API_KEY' }, body: JSON.stringify({ situation: userPreferences.situation, duration: userPreferences.duration, voice_preference: userPreferences.voice, intensity: userPreferences.intensity, background_preference: userPreferences.background, user_id: getCurrentUserId() // For personalization }) }); const result = await response.json(); // Handle the response if (result.status === 'success') { displayAudioPlayer(result.audio_url); saveToUserLibrary(result.session_id); } } Monetization Implementation Strategy Revenue Streams & Pricing Tier\tFeatures\tMonthly Price\tCredits/Month Free\t3 sessions, basic voices\t$0\t3 audio generations Personal\t30 sessions, premium voices, saved library\t$9.99\t30 generations + storage Professional\tUnlimited, custom voices, API access\t$29.99\tUnlimited + white-label Enterprise\tTeam accounts, analytics, integrations\t$99.99\tCustom + priority support Usage Tracking Implementation Copy // N8n Usage Tracking Node const userCredits = await checkUserCredits($json.user_id); if (userCredits.remaining <= 0) { return { json: { error: \"Credit limit exceeded\", upgrade_url: \"https://yourapp.com/upgrade\", status: \"payment_required\" } }; } // Deduct credit after successful generation await decrementUserCredits($json.user_id, 1); Advanced Features & Extensions Personalization En